{"tid":1868862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國將提供1億美元協助中國及其他國家應對疫情","createTime":"2020-02-07T21:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T04:06:03.000Z","uid":125193,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"32c53bf0f7d7a9ebb3a510cab1cebac1b8e272ec","tid":1868862,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:42:05.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧宣布，美國將會提供1億美元資金，直接或透過多邊組織，協助中國及其他受新型冠狀病毒疫情影響的國家。<br />\n<br />\n他說，有關承諾聯同美國私人機構捐出的數億美元，<strong>顯示美國應對疫情的強大領導能力，鼓勵其他國家跟隨。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">蓬佩奧又說，美國已經向中國捐贈近17.8噸醫療用品，包括口罩、防護衣、紗布及呼吸器。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507367-20200208.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507367-20200208.htm&d=%2FXNhycaKVB9NPWqbniWxn3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=ae77da56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1507367-20200208.htm&h=a7218dcd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1507367-20200208.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e3dcc22b243762997e10d2f1384a86f73ca3c972","tid":1868862,"uid":88743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:44:29.000Z","msg":"俾乞兒咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9199cafbef088c0c8b1f2e32ef3f21d3e7c4660c","tid":1868862,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:47:25.000Z","msg":"人哋話什麼都不缺....."},{"pid":"b08beed38012a5ace7715e30217a117139435c27","tid":1868862,"uid":85461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:50:06.000Z","msg":"跟住第二階段叫妳還"},{"pid":"56abd86d384b486f6b3af18985fd77a013a2d4a9","tid":1868862,"uid":8636,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T21:50:07.